三大运营商、手机品牌商、手机供应链最新数据，长期追踪和洞察中国手机通信产业链发展趋势。在市场剧变的2021年结束之时，特别推出《中国手机通信产业数据观察报告（2021）》。 数据显示，2021年，我国电信业务收入累计完成1.47万亿元，比上年增长8.0%，实现自2014年来较高增长水平。此外我国5G基站建设持续推进。截至2021年底，我国建成全球最大5G网，覆盖全国所有地级市城区、超过98%的县城城区和80%的乡镇镇区。 手机及芯片产销量解析：手机市场格局重构，国内手机竞争加剧 据CINNO Research月度国内手机销量监测数据显示，2021年中国市场智能手机销量约3.14亿部，同比上升3%。手机通信产业年度观察：华为淡出后市场格局重构 手机整体销量不及预期"},"attached_info":"Cj8IluHB5Nu99oQbEAMaCDc2NDk5NDg1IIWj1I8GMB84sARAGnIJNTEzOTgxMTQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-b540f328ec0b0641cde1dc7662d56777_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1643868660.8029613","card_id":"Q_514334348","target":{"id":514334348,"title":"客观地说，《四海》拍得到底怎么样？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/514334348","type":"question","created":1643709770,"answer_count":84,"follower_count":110,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4554,12795,711026,1884365,1891059],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"感觉两极分化挺严重的，说难看的挺多的，也有挺多博主说好看的，客观评价，四海怎么样，是不是黑子在黑"},"attached_info":"Cj4IluHB5Nu99oQbEAMaCDc2NTc3ODk3IMqK5I8GMAQ4bkAbcgk1MTQzMzQzNDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b2d1bce1d7f1695728d143839c1bc031_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1643868660.8033674","card_id":"Q_513729289","target":{"id":513729289,"title":"孩子快两岁了，特别嚣张，谁都敢打，说也不听，我应该怎么去正确引导他？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/513729289","type":"question","created":1643299979,"answer_count":195,"follower_count":696,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2146,3143,4719,12046,134321],"comment_count